   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Digitalization Nono Project &quot;Il Canto Sospeso&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will work on modernizing the material around the movie about &quot;Il Canto Sospeso&quot;, Luigi Nono&apos;s composition, which is at the core of the Nono Project. The movie has been distributed over 11,000 times to schools across different countries in Europe. The goal is to start a dialog about humanity, tolerance, the importance of peace and the inalienability of human rights. The movie and materials need to be modernized to fit into the modern and faster moving world and allow a wider spread.</narrative>
  </description>
